ICONS

Sizing

Product icons are 48dp, with 1dp edges
System icons are 24dp
2dp for strokes, corner radius
48DP for touch target

Opacity     Icon      Background color
54%     Active icon       Light
26%    Inactive icon      Light
100%    Active icon       Dark
30%    Inactive icon      Dark


TYPOGRAPHY

Roboto - standard font
Headline: Regular 24sp
App bar, Title: Title style, Medium 20sp
Subheading: Regular 16sp (device), 15sp (desktop)
Buttons, Body 2: Medium 14sp, all caps
Body 1: Regular 14sp
Body 1: Regular 14sp (device), 13sp (desktop)
Display 1 (Black 54%): Regular 34sp
                       Regular 45sp
                       Regular 56sp
                       Regular 112sp
           
Text contrast ratios:  Minimum: 4.5:1  | Preferred: 7:1

