METRICS AND KEYLINES        

Status Bar: 24dp
Toolbar: 56dp
Subtitle: 48dp
List item: 72dp
Screen edge left and right margins: 16dp
Content left margin from screen edge: 72dp
Space between content areas: 8dp

These aspect ratios are recommended: 16:9 | 3:2 | 4:3 | 1:1 | 3:4 | 2:3


